    VCardEntryConstructor
    The VCardInterpreter implementation which enables VCardEntryHandler objects to easily handle each vCard entry.
    VCardEntryCounter
    The class which just counts the number of vCard entries in the specified input.

    The VCardInterpreter implementation which aggregates more than one VCardInterpreter objects and make a user object treat them as one VCardInterpreter object.

    Utilities for VCard handling codes.
